             was indicted for <rs id="t18000219-46-off277" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000219-46-off277" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-46-off277" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000219-46-cd278" type="crimeDate">15th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-46-off277 t18000219-46-cd278"></join>, eight pounds weight of beef, value 2s. 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000219-46-victim430" type="victimName">
                     Lydia 
                     Barnes
                  <interp inst="t18000219-46-victim430" type="surname" value="Barnes"></interp>
